<h2>Syncing with Google Calendar</h2>

You can load all of BAMRU's calendar data into your Google Calendar.  Here's how:

<ol>
  <li>Open your Google Calendar
  <li>Find the 'Add v' button on the bottom right corner
  <li>Select the option 'Add by URL'
  <li>Enter <code><%=current_server%>/calendar.ical</code>
</ol>

After that, the calendar data will sync, and you can overlay BAMRU events onto your Google calendars.

